<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>duō shǎo gè qīng chén 迦南844</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 duō shǎo gè qīng chén, duō shǎo gè lí míng,
 wǒ men yī tóng tuán jù, yǔ zhǔ biǎo zhēn qíng.
 duō shǎo gè xīn yuàn, duō shǎo cì de gǎn dòng,
 dōu huà zuò yī dào dào měi lì de cǎi hóng.
 zhǔ yǔ wǒ men yǒu yuē, xiāng yuē zài qí dǎo zhōng.
 zhǔ yǔ wǒ men yǒu yuē, xiāng yuē zài jìng bài zhōng.
 fán yǒu ěr de dōu dāng tīng, fán yǒu ěr de dōu dāng tīng.
 mò rì lín jìn zài shén jiā jǐn zhōng zài jǐn zhōng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>844</hymn_number>
</song>